=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Guides_Tour_of_UGens_ex67 ===

DESCRIPTION: A dark clean sound, with sine_like oscillator character around 501 Hz, featuring punchy attack and dynamic envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally sparse.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: dark
  crest_factor_db: dynamic
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: clean
  spectral_complexity_mean: sparse
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 501.0658
  harmonic_decay_rate: -4.5471
  harmonic_regularity: 0.9930
  pitch_clarity: 24.5909
  inharmonicity: 0.5621
  type: sine_like
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -17.7515
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: Tour of UGens Example 67
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Guides/Tour_of_UGens.html
// Tags: Tour_of_UGens, Guides
// ---
// --- Example 67 ---
{ Blip.ar(Latch.ar(WhiteNoise.ar, Impulse.ar(9)) * 400 + 500, 4, 0.2) }.play;
{ Blip.ar(Latch.ar(SinOsc.ar(0.3), Impulse.ar(9)) * 400 + 500, 4, 0.2) }.play;
